Personal Use and Modpacks

Using this software to play, configure, or enjoy a game is
always permitted. Including this software in modpacks or mod
compilations is explicitly permitted and encouraged, provided
you preserve the software's own documentation and license files
and comply with Attribution. Modpacks may include configuration
